QuestData.Title: Repairing A-Me 01
QuestData.Description: <Suddenly, the robotic gorilla's eyes light up, and it begins to speak.>$b$b"...operational capacity... less than 5%... accidentally... punctured oil reservoir..."$b$b"...use coconut milk... rock... save A-Me 01..."$b$b<A-Me closes her eyes.>
QuestData.LogDescription: You're pretty sure that A-Me 01 has asked you to obtain an Un'Goro Coconut, crack it on the rock nearby, and give her the High Viscosity Coconut Milk.
QuestData.CompletionText: <A-Me 01 has gone into power save mode.>
QuestData.RewardText: You pour the coconut milk into what appears to be A-Me 01's oil reservoir. You hear the sound of gears whirring and actuators firing.
